 z←Deal n;a;i;p
⍝ This from Mike Kent, via comp.lang.apl 1998-03-26
⍝ Deal produces all !n deals of n-of-n items
⍝ with equal probability.
⍝ (given that ? produces a sample from
⍝ a uniform distribution)
 p←?n⍴n
 :For i :In a←⍳n
     a[i,p[i]]←a[p[i],i]
 :EndFor
 z←a
